data.description: Enjoy living on one level! New carpet, fresh paint, and convenient to I-85. This home offers vaulted ceiling and fireplace in the family room, granite in the kitchen, owner's bedroom with private bath, a two car garage, low yard maintenance, all tucked inside the Lexington Park community. Enjoy summers at the private community pool and walkable downtown with a variety of shops, dining, and other entertainment.
